reviewText: I had this DVD sent to an old friend who has always loved horses. Since she has had a couple of strokes, she had a hard time realizing the package was from me and has never told me if she ever looked at the movies. I'm sure when she does she'll enjoy them. I was glad to find something I could send her for such a good price.
summary: I have no idea - it was a gift.
Title: Horse Movie 4 Pack: (Dark Horse, Father's Choice, Horse Crazy, Riding Tornado)

reviewText: Some of these reminded me of the Saturday morning shows I watched as a kid. I know im dating myself but Fury and My friend Flicka comes to mind. they are good stories with good meanings of life. Good for the whole family. I like horses and any horse lover would enjoy these movies.
Title: Horse Movie 4 Pack: (Dark Horse, Father's Choice, Horse Crazy, Riding Tornado)

reviewText: These were all great movies.  They were done well and have very good messages.  I had not heard of three of these.  Movies I will enjoy over and over again.
Title: Horse Movie 4 Pack: (Dark Horse, Father's Choice, Horse Crazy, Riding Tornado)

reviewText: This movie was enjoyable but nothing stood out as being above average.  I like animal movies and so does my grand-daughter.  We are happy that we purchased it and will be able to watch it again when inclined to do so.
Title: Horse Movie 4 Pack: (Dark Horse, Father's Choice, Horse Crazy, Riding Tornado)

reviewText: I enjoyed all the movies, Father's Choice and Tiding Tornado were my favorite. Good family pictures with life lessons and choices to then talk about.
summary: If you love horses you will like these movies.
Title: Horse Movie 4 Pack: (Dark Horse, Father's Choice, Horse Crazy, Riding Tornado)

reviewText: Fun horse movies for the horse lover.
Title: Horse Movie 4 Pack: (Dark Horse, Father's Choice, Horse Crazy, Riding Tornado)
